  "Description": {
    "English": "A signal receiver and amplifier, tuned to the wavelength of the unconscious mind. It is every color all at once, splitting the surrounding light into a shimmering rainbow.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning:</span> Carrying this antenna into deep space may attract the attention of <span class=\"name name-special\">cosmic megafauna</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个信号接收放大器，根据无意识思维的波长进行调整。它同时具有各种颜色，能将周遭的光线分割成一道道闪亮的彩虹。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：携带此天线进入深空可能会引起<span class=\"name name-special\">宇宙巨型生物的注意</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個訊號接收器和放大器，調諧至無意識思維的波長。它同時呈現出每一種顏色，將周圍的光線分成閃閃發光的彩虹。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>攜帶此天線進入深空可能會引起<span class=\"name name-special\">宇宙巨型動物</span>的注意。"
  },
